@NODE OPTED "The OptionsEditor"

			The OptionsEditor
			-----------------

	General:

	· Mirror	-	On/Off Default is On
	· Stars		-	On/Off Default is On
	· TopCopper	-	On/Off Default is On
	· BottomCopper	-	On/Off Default is On
	· CubeType	-	3D-Box/3D-Plate/Off Default is 3D-Box
	· CubeZoom	-	On/Off Default is Off
	· Jump		-	High/Low/Off/Circle/Low x2/Low x3/High x2 Default is High
	· CopperBar	-	On/Off Default is Off
	· Squares	-	On/Off Default is Off (Slow)
	· Animation	-	On/Off Default is Off


	Cube:

	· Distance	-	Distance can be changed between 0 to 800
	· X-Speed	-	Y-speed can be changed between 0 to 50
	· Y-Speed	-	X-speed can be changed between 0 to 50

	Stars:

	· StarsNum	-	Number of stars can be changed between 0 to 100
	· StarSpeed	-	Starspeed can be changed between 0 to 500

	ScrollText:

	· Y-Pos		-	Y-Pos of scrolltext can be changed between 0 to 200

	Squares:

	· Speed		-	The speed of squares can be changed between 0 to 10

	· Save		-	Saves the effectadjustments to a file, filename.Eff
	· Done		-	When you are done to leave the editor


@ENDNODE OPTED


@NODE FONTMAKER "The FontMaker"

			FontMaker V0.2
			--------------

	This program is made to make it easier to make fonts for DemoMaker
	it has an inbuilt error handler which coming up if there 
	are any errors.

	Functions:

	· "Load a Brush" To load one or up to 38 brushes at same time
          	         max recommended depth:2(4 colours)

	· "Load a Font"  To load a font
	· "New"          To clear screen.A requester shows if font is not saved
	· "Save Font"    To save font
	· "View Font"    To view font
	· "About"        Shows the about requester
	· "Quit"         To quit FontMaker

	· "Move Shape"   To move shape
	· "Grid On"      Turn on the grid
	· "Grid Off"     Turn off the grid
	· "Change Grid"  To change gridsize
	· "Scale"        To scale the brush (ex widthx2 heightx2)
			 !! WARNING !! NEVER USE width x 0 height x 0 IT CRASH THE PROGRAM AND YOUR COMPUTER !

	· "Redraw"       To redraw all shapes



			How to use FontMaker
			--------------------

	1. You need IFF-brushes of characters A to Z and 0 to 9 and "." and ":"
	   Name brushes as "0" to "9" and "A" to "Z" and ":" as "kolon" and "." as "punkt"

	2. Load the brushes into the FontMaker.Set first brush to 0 and last 38.
	3. Choose path and file of the first character to load or click "Set Dir".
	4. Click "Done".Now all brushes will be loaded and displayed
	5. Now choose "Save Font" and your font is done for use in DemoMaker.


@ENDNODE FONTMAKER


@NODE TUTORIAL "Tutorial"

			Tutorial
			--------
	      
	1.  Start DemoMaker with doubleclicking on the icon
	2.  Click on "Load Logo" button
	3.  Select file "Amiga.iff"
	4.  Click on "Edit Text" button.The scrolltext editor coming up.
	5.  Click on "Load Text" button
	6.  Select file "DM_0.45-BigFont.TXT"
	7.  Click on "Load Font" button
	8.  Click on drawer "BigFonts"
	9.  Select file "Deadz-2c.Font"
	10. Click on "Done" button to leave the editor
	11. Click on "Load Module" button
	12. Select file "mod.Demo"
	13. Click on "Test Demo" button and look what happens.......

	Try to change effects in the Options Editor and look now
	what happens.....

@ENDNODE TUTORIAL


